# releases/

Archival of release documentation for Intent versions 1.2.1 through 2.9.0. Each version directory contains RELEASE_NOTES.md documenting features, improvements, breaking changes, and upgrade instructions. Covers the evolution from STP v1.2.1 through Intent's introduction, agent system maturation, and the Agentic Software Engineering Suite in v2.9.0.

## Dirs

- `1.2.1/` -- STP v1.2.1 release notes (directory-based steel thread organization)
- `2.0.0/` -- Intent v2.0.0 rebrand release with Claude Code agent integration
- `2.1.0/` -- Intent v2.1.0 maintenance release with agent system bug fixes
- `2.2.0/` -- Intent v2.2.0 with fileindex command and enhanced Elixir agent
- `2.2.1/` -- Intent v2.2.1 maintenance release for dependency management
- `2.3.2/` -- Intent v2.3.2 with Elixir antipattern detection (24 patterns)
- `2.3.3/` -- Intent v2.3.3 maintenance release
- `2.4.0/` -- Intent v2.4.0 with skills system and upgrade command
- `2.5.0/` -- Intent v2.5.0 with work package management and Highlander audit
- `2.9.0/` -- Intent v2.9.0 Agentic Software Engineering Suite (rules library, critic subagents, extensions)
